name: Evil Forest Survivor Hidden Objects
description:
Evil Forest Survivor Hidden Objects

Awesome Hidden Objects Based on Forest.
Very Difficult Level. You have to find hidden objects very carefully.

If you face any difficulty to find object than 3 type of different hint help you.
3 Different mode to play
- Mountain of Objects : No. of Object to find in this mode.
- Timer Mode : Find Object in particular time period.
- Memory Test : Check your Memory & Observation power.
